channel.title: Need help!Says v0id-pkz on screen while playing. How can I make it BrawlerScape?
channel.description: Hi, I have a v0id-pkz client and I'm trying to edit it to make my own client. Anyways, it says on the bottom-left corner of the screen : v0id-pkz (in white). How can I change that to BrawlerScape? I would appreciate it if someone can help me:). thanks for reading.

item.title: Need help!Says v0id-pkz on screen while playing. How can I make it BrawlerScape?
item.dc:creator: @nl_pker nl pker
item.description:
@nl_pker wrote:

[quote=“jjones10, post:4, topic:242535”]search in client.java for “@whi@v0id-pkz”
then replace v0id-pkz with BrawlerScape[/quote]

he is right
